snippet: A four-day version of the weeklong fitness program created by The Ranch at Live Oak will be offered in September at the Four Seasons Westlake Village in Southern California.
abstract: A four-day version of the weeklong fitness program created by The Ranch at Live Oak will be offered in September at the Four Seasons Westlake Village in Southern California.
lead_paragraph: The Ranch at Live Oak, the popular weeklong fitness program in Malibu, Calif., is beginning a four-day version this September at the Four Seasons Westlake Village in the nearby Conejo Valley.
